Context

We will be exploring the dataset of 522,517 recipes categorized in 312 classes. Data includes information about each recipe like cooking times, servings, ingredients, nutrition, instructions, and more. We will also be covering its comments, including 1,401,982 reviews from 271,907 different users. This dataset provides information about the author, rating, review text, and more.

Making sense

Whenever we are working with a new dataset, it make sense to start by getting a broad view of the data. We can:

  • Plot the number of recipies by creation date
  • Understand the ratings given over time
  • Check how many authors contributed so far
  • Explore the most popular categories
  • Description length over time (?)

Feel free to click any of the options above to start exploring!
